&lt;p&gt;Demolition work shall be carried out by hand tools or by tools held in the hand, 
other than power-driven tools.
REASON: To preserve the special interest of the listed building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No plumbing or pipes, other than rainwater pipes, shall be fixed to the external 
faces of the building unless shown on the approved drawings.
REASON: To preserve the special interest of the listed building.&lt;/p&gt;
